{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Hitler rounded them up if they didn't believe it, and would send them to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was how Dachau was built in the first place, to-- for the opponents of the Reich.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, things-- not specifically after Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things had-- had-- had happened before that already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But number one, I didn't mention that when I was 14 years old, after I had to leave school, I was fortunate enough to-- taken in by some man who-- who taught me the building-- the designing and building of furniture.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in an apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And four years afterwards, in 1939, I had a chance to finish it yet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I became a furniture designer and furniture-- and furniture builder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this was, first of all my-- that's when, I said, with my bicycle I went to the workplace.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my workplace that I referred to earlier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Things started to get tighter before the Kristallnacht already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, the thumb screws were tightened little by little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, in my lectures that I am holding often, I'm calling this the process of dehumanization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which started to take place little by little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, from the time on, in my school and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I say, by that time, Jewish people had lost their jobs all over the places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The unemployment among Jewish people was just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So pretty soon, the order was given that Jews were not allowed to go to any public places.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No restaurants, no movie-- no theaters, no concerts, my beloved soccer games.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nowhere.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go anyplace anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A curfew was declared, that Jews had to be home in the winter, at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
